1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,647
Before moving into the day, pause.

2
00:00:02,647 --> 00:00:05,201
Take one slow breath in.

3
00:00:08,201 --> 00:00:09,919
And let it out.

4
00:00:09,919 --> 00:00:16,142
Ask yourself: What quality of Self-energy
do I want to practice today?

5
00:00:22,142 --> 00:00:22,142
<break time="3s" />

6
00:00:22,142 --> 00:00:28,919
Maybe calm, curiosity, compassion,
clarity, courage, confidence, creativity,

7
00:00:28,919 --> 00:00:30,455
or connectedness.

8
00:00:30,455 --> 00:00:31,477
Choose one.

9
00:00:31,477 --> 00:00:35,749
Now ask: Where might I need this quality
today?

10
00:00:41,749 --> 00:00:41,749
<break time="3s" />

11
00:00:41,749 --> 00:00:44,628
Let one situation come to mind.

12
00:00:44,628 --> 00:00:47,414
Imagine bringing that quality with you.

13
00:00:53,414 --> 00:00:53,414
<break time="3s" />

14
00:00:53,414 --> 00:00:54,575
Not perfectly.

15
00:00:54,575 --> 00:00:56,479
Just enough to remember.

16
00:00:56,479 --> 00:01:03,835
Silently say: Today, I will practice
returning to this quality. One moment at

17
00:01:03,835 --> 00:01:04,513
a time.

18
00:01:10,513 --> 00:01:10,513
<break time="3s" />

19
00:01:10,513 --> 00:01:11,813
Take one more breath.

20
00:01:11,813 --> 00:01:12,649
And begin.

